{{orphan|date=January 2011}}
'''Universal Annuity System''' is when an [[international community]] (e.g. the [[United Nations|UN]]) establishes a [[Funding|fund]] that the governments or communities of the world add to every year. These funds are invested.  The gains on these [[investment]]s are distributed evenly among the people as [[income]].  This process is known as the Universal Annuity System. A [[sovereign wealth fund]] at an international level.

